<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>hl lyswʿ mn mtẖyl</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- hal̊ līasūʿa min̊ matẖīl̊
 fī ạlṭũh̊ri wāl̊jamāl̊?
 fī sẖakẖ̊ṣi dẖā ạl̊fādī ạl̊farīd̊
 tajasãma ạl̊kamāl̊

[V2]
 ạlqrạr: (lạ laẙsa mitẖ̊luhu .. qad̊ fāqa maj̊duhu
 qal̊bī yuḥibũhu .. wayab̊gẖī qur̊bahu)2

[V3]
 2- hal̊ līasūʿa min̊ matẖīl̊
 man̊ ḍaḥãy̱ biạl̊maj̊di?
 maʿ̊ ạảnãhu ạlrãbũ ạl̊majīd̊
 qad̊ ʿāsẖa kāl̊ʿab̊di

[V4]
 3- hal̊ līasūʿa min̊ matẖīl̊
 man̊ jāda bidimāh̊?
 kulũ ḥayātī waqūāẙ
 lahu maday̱ ạl̊ḥayāh̊</lyrics>
<author>trnymạt rwḥyẗ</author>
</song>